\h Fofozir Gumazim 
\toc3 FG 
\toc2 Fofozir Gumazim 
\toc1 Fofozir Gumazim Ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n M…®ngarim Buri 
\mt1 Fofozir Gumazim Ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n M…®ngarim Buri 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Eklisiastis 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n, fofozir gumazir mam uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n gun m…®gei. Fofozir gumazir kam a bizir av…®ribagh n…®ghn…®si. A deraghav…®ra gumazamizibar gara me asavsuisi. Egha a bizir bar av…®ribar garima, da os…®mt…®zim an navim gan…®di. Egha a gumazamizibar ik…®r…®m…®ribar gari, da bar otevegha derazir puvat…®. Bizir bar av…®rir gumazamiziba amiba, dar dagher aghuitam otivir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n fofozir gumazir kam kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ik…®r…®m…®rir gumazamiziba itir kam, an m…®ngariba puvat…®. 
\ip Godra, a ik…®r…®m…®rir kam…®n Afeziam. Ez…® e gumazamiziba, e deragh God…®n Arazibagh foghan kogham. Kamagh…®n akar gavgavir kabanang, e da baragh dar aghuaghan kogham. Ez…® fofozir gumazir kam kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze, ia dar am…®raghan mark…®. Manmagh amiz…® e deragha fozir puvat…®, God nguazir kam…®n ikiasa dughiar otevim vaghvagha e gan…®ngi, eght…® dughiar kam…®n aven e nguazir kam…®n ik…® pamtem ingar…®va bar akongegham. Kamagh…®n deragham. 
\ip Gumazir av…®riba God…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven ak…®nafarir mam…®n gari, akar kamagh…®n gariba an aven itima, me an gara d…®gavir kuram gami. Egha ak…®nafarir kam bizir mam en aka, a kamak…®n. Gumazir manam os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateri, a uaghan God…®n adarazir aven ikiam. Ak…®nafarir kam gumazamizir bar av…®ribar akura. Guizbang…®ra, me uari os…®mt…®ziba ikia n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami. Fofozir gumazir kam osiriz…® mogh…®n, bizir kaba me batifi. Egha me ak…®nafarir kam…®n garir dughiam…®n, me kamagh…®n fo, me uarira itir puvat…®. Me God…®n adarazir aven iti. Ez…® bizir kaba me gamima me uam God me bagha d…®k…®r…®zir akar God…®n ak…®nafarim…®n itibagh n…®ghn…®si. 
\c 1  
\s1 Biziba bar mati pura biziba 
\p  
\v 1 Kar gumazir bar fofozir mam…®n akaba, a Devit…®n otarim, a Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ikia atrivim…®n iti: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 Bar fofozir gumazir kam kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, 
\q1 ‚ÄúBiziba bar, dar m…®ngariba bar mongez…®, 
\q2 bar guizbang…®ra, e dagh fozir puvat…®gha bar okam n…®ghn…®si.‚Äù 
\q1  
\v 3 E bar, overiam…®n apengan itir dughiam…®n 
\q2 e ingangarir m…®t…®abagh amua, egha da ik…®v…®ra ikiamin ivezir aghuir manabara isi? 
\q2 Puvat…®. Da tong bar en akurvazir puvat…®. 
\q1  
\v 4 Gumazamiziba ovia zui ez…® igiaba otiva men danganiba isima, 
\q2 nguazir kam kamagh…®ra iti. 
\q1  
\v 5 E garima, aruem anaga uaghira zuam…®ra ivemara uamategha 
\q2 an anadir danganim…®n zui. 
\q1  
\v 6 E gari, am…®nim saut…®n amadaghan ivava anaga not…®n amadaghan vua uaghiri. 
\q2 Egha a kamagh…®ram amua ghuav…®ra iti. 
\q1  
\v 7 E gari, faneba bar em…®ra ongarimra uaghiri, ez…® ongarim izevir puvat…®. 
\q2 Egha g…®n d…®paba uamategha ghua d…®par suiabar ghuegha uamategha em…®ra ua izaghiri. 
\q1  
\v 8 Nguazir kam…®n biziba bar zurara ghuav…®ra itima e dar gara dagh n…®ghn…®gha bar dar am…®ra. 
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, e bizir kabar am…®rvagha dar gun m…®k…®mamin m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh asa. 
\q2 E bizir kabar garir ifongiam a gevir puvat…®, e pura dar gara kamagh…®ra iti. 
\q2 E bizir kaba barazir ifongiam a gevir puvat…®, e da baraghav…®ra iti. 
\q1  
\v 9 Bizir fom…®ram otiviziba, da g…®n uam otivam. 
\q2 Bizir God fom…®ram amiziba, a ua dar amuam. 
\q2 Bizir igiatam, overiam…®n apengan itir puvat…®. 
\q1  
\v 10 Dughiar mabar gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gan, kar bizir igiar mam.‚Äù 
\q2 Ez…® puvat…®. 
\q2 Bizir kaba bar, fom…®ra e nguazir kam…®n t…®ghar otivamin dughiam…®n, da iti. 
\q1  
\v 11 Fom…®ram en inazibar dughiam…®n otivizir biziba, gumazitam dagh in…®r…®ghan kogham. 
\q2 Eght…® gumazamizir en g…®n otivamiba, 
\q2 me e gin…®r…®ghan kogham. 
\s1 Fofozir ekiam, a pura bizim 
\p  
\v 12 K…® fofozir gumazim, k…® Israelian atrivim ikia, Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ike.  
\v 13 K…® overiam…®n apengan otivir bizibar fofozim iniasa dagh n…®ghn…®si, egh k…® deraghv…®ra dagh n…®ghn…®gh dar m…®ngarim g…®foghasa. Guizbang…®ra, ingangarir God e gumazamiziba en boribagh an…®ngizir kam, a bar oseme.  
\v 14 Overiam…®n apengan otivir biziba bar, k…® deraghav…®ra dar ganigha egha k…® kamagh…®n fo, bar guizbang…®ra, gumazamiziba amir biziba bar, dar m…®ngariba bar mongez…®, e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. Da mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghua, an suighan ibura. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 15 Bizir ik…®z…®righa g…®vaziba, e da am…®nan iburagham. 
\q2 Ez…® bizir puvat…®ziba, e da mengan kogham. 
\b  
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Atriviba 4:29-31\x*K…® uab…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, k…® fofozir bar dafam iti, nan fofozim fom…®ra Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n atrivim…®n ikezir atrivibar fofozibagh afira. K…® fofozir aghuim inigha g…®vagha, n…®ghn…®zir aghuir av…®ribagh fo.  
\v 17 K…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim pamtem…®n a buria ingara, uaghan onganizir arazim…®n m…®ngarim buria ghuava am…®ra. K…® puram ingangarir dafam gamigha dat…®r…®gh…®n fogha g…®vagha ghaze, arazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim iniamim, a mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghua an suighan ibura. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Fofozir Gumazim 12:12\x*Bar guizbang…®ra, gumazir fofozir av…®riba itim, a n…®ghn…®zir av…®riba aterima da aneb…®ri. 
\q2 Ez…® an fofozim ghua bar ekevegha, uaghan os…®mt…®zir av…®riba a gan…®di. 
\c 2  
\s1 Agoroger araziba, dar m…®ngariba puvat…® 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® k…® uab…®ra uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, K…® agoroger arazim deraghv…®ra a tuis…®gh ganigh fogh suam, a ti guizbang…®ra dera o puvat…®? Egha k…® inivaf…®zim…®n agoroger arazibar uan ifongiam ag…®vasa dagh n…®ghn…®si. Egha k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, a uaghan an m…®ngariba bar mongez…®, e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 2 K…® kamagh…®n fo, akazir arazim, an arazir onganim. Ez…® agoroger arazim tong en akurvazir puvat…®.  
\v 3 K…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghasa ingarav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n, k…® inivaf…®zir agoroger arazim bagha wain…®n d…®paba apir arazim gamua a tuis…®si. K…® kamagh…®n foghasa, gumazamiziba dughiar otevim…®n overiam…®n apengan ik…®t…®, bizir manamra men akuragham? 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4-8 \xt 1 Atriviba 10:23-27; 2 Eghaghaniba 9:22-27\x*K…® ingangarir av…®rir dafabagh amiz…® gumazamiziba da bagha ziar ekiam na gan…®di. Ez…® k…® ua bagha d…®penir bar dafabagh amuava, wain…®n azenibar ingari.  
\v 5 K…® azenibar ingara da opari, ez…® dar aven temer dagher aghuiba batiba iti.  
\v 6 Egha k…® uan temer av…®rir kaba ruasa ua bagha mozir d…®par ekiabagh kui.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Atriviba 4:23\x*K…® ua bagh pura ingangarir gumazir k…®niba ko amizir k…®nibagh ivese. Ez…® men boriba, nan d…®penim…®n aven nan ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®n iti. Ez…® k…® bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n av…®riba iti. Gumazir fom…®ra Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n itiba, nan m…®n bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n av…®riba itir puvat…®.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1 Atriviba 10:10; 10:14-22\x*K…® ua bagha gol ko silvan dag…®ar av…®riba isi. Ez…® kantrin igharazibar atriviba ko provins…®n igharazibar gumazir dapaniba, me uan dag…®aba isa na bagha da amadi. Ez…® k…® ighiabagh amir gumazamiziba, me na bagha ighiabagh ami. Egha k…® amuir dozir av…®riba iti, ez…® me na damut…® nan navim bar deragham. Gumaziba bar, arazir kam bagh bar akongegham. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 29:25\x*K…® bizir kaba bar da iniz…®, da na gamima nan ziam bar ekefe. Ez…® fom…®ra Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazitam nan m…®n bizir aghuir av…®ritaba itir puvat…®. Nan fofozir aghuiba uaghan, na atagh…®razir puvat…®, da na ko ikiav…®ra iti.  
\v 10 K…® tong uan ifongiam d…®kab…®razir pu. Bar puvat…®. K…® bizir manam gifonge, k…® puram a iniam. Egha k…® amizir ingangarir kaba bagha bar akonge. Ez…® agoroger kam, a kamak…®n, a nan ingangarim…®n ivezim.  
\v 11 Egha g…®n k…® uan dafarimning…®n ingarizir bizir kaba bar dar gara, da tuis…®gha deraghav…®ra dagh n…®ghnigha ghaze, bizir kaba, dar m…®ngariba bar mongez…®, e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. Da mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghua, an suighan ibura. Ia oragh, e bar, overiam…®n apengan itir dughiam…®n e ingangarir m…®t…®abagh ami, eght…® da pura mang…® dar dagher aghuiba puvat…®gham. Da tong en akuraghan kogham. 
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir aghuim mati pura bizim 
\p  
\v 12 K…® bizir kabagh amigha g…®fa, eght…® g…®n gumazir igharazitam nan danganim inigh atrivim…®n otogh, a bizir igharazir manatam damuam? Bar puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim…®n m…®ngariba ko arazir onganibar m…®ngaribagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 13 K…® n…®ghnigha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n fo, n…®ghn…®zir aghuim, an arazir onganiba bar dagh afira, mati aruem…®n angazangarim m…®tarmem gafira.  
\v 14 Fofozir gumazamiziba me deragha tuavim…®n garava an zui. Ez…® gumazamizir onganiba, mati gumaziba m…®tarmem…®n tuavim…®n zui. Bizir kam a guizbang…®ra, ez…® k…® n…®ghn…®gha ghua n…®ghn…®zir ekiar mam na bato. A kamak…®n, aning uaghara ovevem aning bativam. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® k…® uab…®ra uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, bizir gumazir onganiba batozim, uaghan na bativam. Kamagh…®n, nan fofozir av…®rir kaba, manmagh…®n nan akuragham? Bar puvat…®gham. Egha k…® uan navir averiam…®n aven kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, fofozir aghuim uaghan, an m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 16 K…® fo, gumazamizir g…®n izamiba, me bar e g…®n amadagham. Guizbang…®ra, gumazir onganiba ko gumazir fofoziba itiba, me uam e gin…®r…®ghan kogham. Ez…® ovevem…®n dughiam, fofozir gumazim, gumazir onganim gafiraghan kogham. Puvat…®. E bar mogh…®ram ovengam!  
\v 17 Ez…® bizir overiam…®n apengan otivir kaba bar mogh…®ram os…®mt…®zim nan navim gan…®di. Kamagh…®n, k…® uan ik…®r…®m…®rim bar an aghua. Bizir kaba bar, dar m…®ngariba aven mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. Da mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuava, an suighan ibura. 
\s1 Ingangarir m…®t…®abar m…®ngariba ko dagheba puvat…® 
\p  
\v 18 K…® overiam…®n apengan ikia zurara puv…®ra ingari. Egha k…® fogha g…®fa, ingangarir m…®tiar k…® amizir kaba, gumazir igharazim iz…® nan danganim inigh dar ganam. Kamagh…®n, k…® ingangarir kaba bar dar aghua.  
\v 19 Eght…® gumazir nan danganim iniamim, k…® a g…®fozir pu, a ti gumazir fofozim itim, o gumazir onganim. Egh a iz…®, k…® uan fofozir aghuim…®n overiam…®n apengan amizir ingangarir m…®tiar kabar ganigh dar ghuavim…®n ikegham. Ez…® arazir kam, uaghan an m…®ngarim modoz…®, e a g…®fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 20 Kamagh…®n, k…® overiam…®n apengan ikia ingangarir m…®tiar amizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gha nan navim ikuvigha bar oseme.  
\v 21 E garima, gumazir maba, fofoziba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ikia egha uan fofozir kam ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuir kam sara ingara biziba deragha dagh amua, bizir bar av…®riba isi. Egha me g…®n ariaghirez…®, gumazir igharaziba pura men biziba isi, me men m…®n fofozir kamagh gariba itir puvat…®. Arazir kam a derazir puvat…®, egha uaghan an m…®ngarim aven modoz…® e a g…®fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 22 E zurara overiam…®n apengan ikia puv ingarava bizir av…®riba uaghan dagh n…®ghn…®si, ez…® bizir kam ik…®v…®ra ikiamin ivezir aghuir manatam e ikaragham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Jop 5:7; 14:1\x*Dughiar e nguzim…®n itir kaba, m…®zaziba e batifi, ez…® en ingangariba os…®mt…®ziba e gan…®di. Ez…® e uaghan d…®magaribar dakuasa amua, dagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ikia avughsaziba en puvat…®. Ez…® arazir kam uaghan, an m…®ngarim modoz…® e a g…®fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Fofozir Gumazim 3:13; 5:17; 9:7; Aisaia 56:12; Luk 12:19; 1 Korin 15:32\x*Arazir mam bar dera, egha arazir igharazibagh afira. A kamak…®n: E pamtem ingarigh egh uan ingangaribar dagheba ini dar am…®va, dagh ifongegh bar akuegham. K…® arazir kam…®n gara egha fo, bizir aghuir kaba en biziba pu. Bar puvat…®, God uab…® bizir kabar afeziam, egha a da isa e gan…®di.  
\v 25 Guizbang…®ra, God puvat…®ght…®, e manmagh…®n dam…®, bar akuegh…®va arazir kabar amuam? Bar puvat…®gham.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 2:26 \xt Jop 32:8; Aghuzir Akaba 2:6\x*Guizbang…®ra, God ifongezir gumazamiziba, a n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozim ko, bar akuegha itir arazim me gan…®di. Ez…® arazir kurabagh ami darasi, a me gamima, me ingara dagheba ko biziba isa da akumakua da isa God ifongez…® darazigh an…®di. Arazir kam, uaghan an m…®ngarim modoz…® e a g…®fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. A mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuava an suighan ibura. 
\c 3  
\s1 Biziba bar mogh…®ra, vaghvagh otivamin dughiaba iti 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Fofozir Gumazim 3:17; 8:6\x*Overiam…®n apengan otivir biziba vaghvagha, da uan dughiabaram otifi: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Hibru 9:27\x*Amiziba otamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 ez…® e bar ar…®m…®ghiramin dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha e dagheba oparamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e dagheba asiamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1  
\v 3 Egha e gumazibav soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiramin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e me damut…® me ghuamaghamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha e biziba angarar…®ghamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e bizibar ingaramin dughiaba iti. 
\q1  
\v 4 Egha e aziamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e akam…®n dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha e bizibagh n…®ghn…®gh navim ikuvamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e bar akongegh ighiabar amuamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ez…® paba uan amuiba ko dakuamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh aning uaning ko dakuan koghamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha paba uan amuibar suighamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh an suighan koghamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1  
\v 6 Egha e bizir ovengeziba buriamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh da buri mang…® da ateghamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha e biziba deraghv…®ra dar ar…®ghamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e pura da makunamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1  
\v 7 Egha e korotiaba ab…®ghrar…®ghamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e da isamamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha e m…®k…®man kogh n…®m…®ra ikiamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e m…®k…®mamin dughiam iti. 
\q1  
\v 8 Egha e igharaz darazi bar me gifongeghamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh e men aghuaghamin dughiaba iti. 
\q1 Egha e igharaz daraziv soghamin dughiaba iti, 
\q2 egh me ko derav…®ra dapiamin dughiaba iti. 
\b  
\p  
\v 9 Gumazamizir ingangaribagh amiba, me bar ik…®v…®ra ikiamin ivezir aghuir manabar uan ingangarir me amiba bagha da isi?  
\v 10 God e gan…®ngizir ingangaribar os…®mt…®ziba, k…® deraghav…®ra dar ganigha dagh fogha g…®fa.  
\v 11 God, biziba bar otivamin dughiabar ak…®ri, egha dagh amiz…® da uan dughiar aghuim…®n otivigha bar deragha ganganir aghuibagh ami. Ez…® God uaghan en n…®ghn…®zibagh amiz…®, e uan navibar aven n…®ghn…®gha, bar fom…®ra itir bizir otiviziba ko bar g…®n otivamibagh fofoghasa n…®ghn…®si. Egh God fom…®ram amizir biziba ko g…®n damuamin biziba, e deraghv…®ra dagh foghan kogham.  
\v 12 K…® bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gha ghua kamagh…®n fo, arazir mam, arazir igharazibagh afira. Arazir kam, a kamak…®n, e nguazir kam…®n itir dughiam…®n, e arazir aghuibar amu bar akuegh ikiam.  
\v 13 Egh e uan ingangarir e amizibar ivezim ini daghebar am…® bar akuegh ikiam. Bizir kaba, God e gan…®dir bizir aghuiba. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Jems 1:17\x*K…® fo, God…®n Araziba ik…®v…®ra ik…®, egh g…®vaghan kogham. Puvat…®. Da kamagh…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Gumazitam uan arazitam God…®n arazitam gis…®n dat…®ghan kogham. Egh gumazitam ua God…®n arazitam batueghan kogham. God gumazamiziba an atiating an apengan ikiasa, a kamagh…®n ami.  
\v 15 Bizir dat…®r…®gh…®n otiviba, da fom…®ram otifis. Ez…® bizir g…®n otivamiba, da uaghan fom…®ram otivigha g…®fa. God fom…®ram otivizir biziba ataghiz…®, da bar ghuezir puvat…®. A bizir kabagh ami da uam otifi. 
\s1 Gumazamizibar araziba derazir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® k…® arazir mam…®n garima a uaghan overiam…®n apengan iti. E fo, jasba kotiam…®n aven arazir aghuibar g…®nt…®gh deraghv…®ra gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba tuis…®gham. Ez…® puvat…®, me arazir aghuibar g…®nt…®zir pu. Bar puvat…®. Me dughiar maba arazir bar kurabar g…®nt…®si.  
\v 17 Ez…® k…® ua kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, God gumazamiziba kotiam dar…®ghamin dughiam…®n, a gumazamizir an damazim…®n deraziba ko gumazamizir kuraba, a me bagh dughiam at…®gh, men araziba tuis…®gham.  
\v 18 Egha k…® uaghan kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, God gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®ght…®, me kamagh…®n fogh suam, e gumazamiziba, en araziba uaghan as…®zibar arazibar m…®n iti.  
\v 19 K…® ghaze, E gumazamiziba uaghan as…®zibar m…®n ovengam. As…®ziba ovei, ez…® e gumazamiziba uaghan ovei. Gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba uagharam ik…®r…®m…®rir angam…®ra itim an…®dir am…®nim ikia, arua bizibagh ami, egha aning uaghara ik…®r…®m…®rir kam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n, gumazamizibar ik…®r…®m…®rim as…®zibar ik…®r…®m…®rim gafirazir puvat…®. Aning…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n m…®ngarim uaghara aning…®n modoz…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Jenesis 3:19\x*Gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba uaghara, ovea ghua nguazim…®n zui. E fo, God nguazir m…®nemeniam inigha, gumazim…®n inivaf…®zim…®m ingari. Kamagh…®n, an aremegh, uamategh nguazir m…®nemeniam gavagham.  
\v 21 Ez…®, gumazir maba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazim aremez…® an duam God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanadima, as…®zim…®n duam nguazim…®n ghuaghiri. Ez…® tinara bizir kam…®n ganigh a g…®fogham? 
\p  
\v 22 K…® bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghua kamagh…®n fo, arazir mam arazir igharazibagh afira. Arazir kam a kamak…®n. Ingangarir e amiba, e dar gan dagh ifongegh bar akuegh ikiam. Bar akongezir arazir kam, a ivezir aghuir God e bagha m…®sevezimra. Ez…® tinara, e ar…®m…®ghiregh g…®vaght…® en g…®n otivamin biziba en akagham? 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Overiam…®n apengan itir bizir gumazamiziba amiba, k…® ua dagh n…®ghn…®gha fo, da derazir puvat…®. Gumazir kuraba gumazamiziba d…®kab…®ra os…®mt…®ziba me gar…®zima, me bar puv…®ram arai. Ez…® men akurvaghan gumaziba puvat…®. K…® gari, gavman…®n gavgavim, gumazir kurabaram akurvasi. Kamagh…®n, gavman uaghan men akurvazir puvat…®.  
\v 2 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazamizir ovengeziba, me bar dera, me nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibar m…®n os…®mt…®ziba aterir puvat…®. Oveaghuezibar dabirabim, an angam…®ra itir gumazamizibar dabirabim gafira.  
\v 3 Ez…® gumazamizir t…®ghar nguazim…®n otivamiba, me arazir kurar gumazamiziba overiam…®n apengan amibar ganizir pu. Kamagh…®n me bar dera, egha gumazamizir nguazim…®n itibagh afira. 
\p  
\v 4 Egha k…® uaghan arazir mam…®n gari, gumazamiziba ingangarir m…®t…®abagh amua, bizir aghuibagh ami. Ez…® bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, me uan namakabar garima, me bizir av…®riba ikia ziar ekiaba isima, me uaghan men m…®n otivasa ingangarir av…®ribagh ami. Ez…® k…® ghaze, arazir kam uaghan an m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. A mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuava an suighan ibura.  
\v 5 Marazi ghaze, gumazir ingangaribar amuan am…®ragha pura nguibam…®n itim, a gumazir onganim. Egh an gavgavim g…®vaght…® an aremegham.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 15:16-17; 16:8\x*Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, kamagh…®n dera, e bizir muziariba ik…®, navir am…®rizim sara ikiam. Gumazir maba bizir av…®riba bagha n…®ghn…®gha pamtem ingara os…®mt…®zir av…®riba sara iti, ez…® arazir kam ikufi, mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuava an suighan ibura. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® k…® ua garima, arazir igharazir mam overiam…®n apengan iti, a uaghan an m…®ngarim modoz…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 8 A kamak…®n, gumazir mam a uab…®ra iti, egha boriba ko aveghbuaba puvat…®gha ingarav…®ra ikia avughsaziba an puvat…®. Egha a bizir bar av…®riba ikia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, bizir kaba t…®ghar nan ifongiam ag…®vagham. K…® mang…® zurara ingarv…®ra ikiam. A kamagh uab…® uab…® m…®geir puvat…®, ‚ÄúK…® tizim bagha pura ingangarir m…®tiar kabagh amua dar daghetam isa pura ikia bar akongezir puvat…®? K…® oveght…® tinara bizir kaba iniam? Puvat…®gham.‚Äù Gumazir kamagh…®n amim…®n araziba, da bar kufi. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, arazir kam uaghan, an m…®ngarim modoz…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 9 Uab…®ra itir arazim, a derazir puvat…®. Gumazir pumuning uaning inigh ik…®t…®, deragham. Eght…® gumazir pumuning uaning inigh ingart…®, aning…®n ingangarim deragham.  
\v 10 Eght…® tav ir…®ght…®, tav an agharim…®n suiragh uam a fegham. Ez…® uab…®ra itir gumazim, gumaka, a ir…®ght…® tina an akuragh a fegham? Bar puvat…®gham.  
\v 11 Gumazir pumuning arugharugh, egh uaning inigh dakuva, aning…®n m…®karzimning fengam. Eght…® tav uab…®ra dakuva, an arugharugham.  
\v 12 Gumazir vam…®ra, an apaniba a m…®sogh bar aneg…®vagham. Ez…® gumazir pumuning, me aning m…®soghan iburagham. Guizbang…®ra gumazitam, benir pumuning ko m…®kezim inigh da ruivigh ikar…®zim g…®right…® da zuam…®ra d…®ghoreghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 13-14 Gumazir igiar biziba puvat…®zitam o kalabuziar gumazir tam, aning…®n tav kantrin atrivim…®n ik…®t…® deragham. Ez…® atrivir igharazir mam bar ghuri, egha a fofozir gumazibar n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba baraghan aghua, ez…® an arazim bar ikuvigha ongani. Guizbang…®ra, atrivir igiar biziba puvat…®zir kam, a n…®ghn…®zir aghuim…®n ikia, atrivir ghurir kam gafira. 
\p  
\v 15 K…® garima, atrivir ghurir kam g…®n aremez…®, gumazir igiam an danganim ini, ez…® overiam…®n apengan tir gumazamiziba bar atrivir igiar kam…®n g…®n zui.  
\v 16 Ez…® gumazir bar av…®rir me men d…®bobonim d…®ponan iburaziba, me bar an apengan itima a me gatifa. Ez…® g…®n an aremez…®, g…®n otivir gumazamiziba, me an amizir bizir ekiar kabagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, uaghan an m…®ngarim modoz…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. Mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuava an suighan ibura.\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Hibrun akam ves 13-16 aning…®n itir akar is…®n zuimning deragha aning ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\c 5  
\s1 N…® pura m…®k…®m akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n God damuan mark…® 
\p  
\v 1 N…® deraghv…®ra uan arazibagh n…®ghnigh…®va, God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…®. Puram aven mangan mark…®. N…® fofozim iniasava aven zui. Egh gumazir mabar m…®n puram ofabar amuan mark…®, mati gumazim fofoziba puvat…®ghava dagh ami. Kamagh…®n amir gumazamiziba, me deragha fozir pu, bizir manam God…®n damazim…®n dera.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 10:19; Matyu 6:7\x*N…® faragh navir averiam…®n aven derav…®ra n…®ghnigh, g…®n d…®kavigh uan akatorim…®n m…®k…®m. Egh n…® God ko m…®geir dughiam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar amuan mark…®. God a gavgavir ekiam ikia uan Nguibam…®n iti, ez…® e gumazir k…®niba nguazir kam…®n iti. Kamagh…®n, n…® an damazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar a damuan mark…®.  
\v 3 E fo, n…® osemegha bizir av…®riba bagha navim isia dagh n…®ghn…®gh, irebabar ganam. Kamagh…®ra n…® puv…®ra m…®geir gumazim, n…® mati gumazir onganim puv…®ra bizibav gei.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt D…®boboniba 30:2; God…®n Araziba 23:21-23; Onger Akaba 66:13-14; 76:11\x*Egh n…® akar d…®k…®r…®z…® tam…®n God damigh…®va, zuam…®ram an g…®n mang…® a damigh. Egh n…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®n mang…® damighan kogh, n…® mati gumazir onganim. God kamagh…®n amir gumazamizibagh ifongezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zim gami, egh n…® an g…®n mang…® a damigh.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 20:25; Aposel 5:4\x*Egha n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n God gamigha an g…®nt…®zir pu, kar arazir aghuim puvat…®, arazir bar kuram. Egh n…® n…®ghnigh fogh suam, n…® uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim g…®nt…®ghan kogham, egh n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam damuan mark…®.  
\v 6 Egh n…® puram akar d…®k…®r…®zim damigh…®va, an g…®n mangan kogh, n…® arazir kuram gami. Egh n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir tam damigh, egh g…®n God…®n ofa gamir gumazim m…®k…®man mark…® suam, ‚ÄúK…® deragha n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha, akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam gami.‚Äù N…® tizim bagh God damight…® an an…®ngagharim n…®n ikiam? N…® kamagh…®n damut…®, a n…®n an…®ngaghegham. Egh n…® ingangarir m…®t…®abagh amua inizir bizibagh as…®ghasigham.  
\v 7 N…® gumazir zurara irebabar garim, o n…® gumazir pura m…®geim, arazir kaba uaghan pura biziba. Arazir kabar m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n, n…® zurara God…®n atiating an apengan ik…®. 
\s1 N…® gumazir dag…®ar av…®riba itim…®n otivs…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…® 
\p  
\v 8 N…® gavman…®n gant…®, a gumazir onganarazibagh amiba os…®mt…®ziba me dar…®gh…®va, men kotiaba deragh da ak…®ran kogh, me ateght…® me deragh dapian koght…®, ia d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. Arazir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Ingangarir gumazir dapaniba arazir kabagh amima, men garir gumazir ekiar maba, men ingangaribar gara os…®mt…®ziba me gar…®si. Ez…® gumazir men garir kaba, me uaghan gumazir ekiar maba ikia men gara os…®mt…®ziba me gar…®si, me arazir kamra me gami.  
\v 9 Egha me arazir kam gamima, gumazamiziba uan nguazibar azenibar ingara dagheba amaga dar iveziba isima me bar men dag…®aba tuiragha uarira uarigh an…®di. Ez…® atrivim uaghan men dag…®ar nar maba isi.\f + \fr 5:9 \ft Hibrun akam deragha ves 9…®n itir akam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 10 Gumazim dag…®ar av…®riba iniasa puv…®ram n…®ghn…®zima, dag…®ar muziarir a isiba, an ifongiam ag…®vaghan kogham. Ez…® gumazim, dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazim…®n m…®n otivs…® n…®ghnigh…®va, bizir a isir kaba, an ifongiam ag…®vaghan kogham. Kamagh…®n, dag…®am bagha bar ifongezir arazim ko bizibagh ifongezir arazim, da uaghan dar m…®ngariba mongez…®, e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 11 Egh gumazim…®n ivezim mavanangt…®, an ik…®zir gumazir av…®rim iz…®va an d…®penim giz…®vagh an daghebar amam. Kamagh…®n, gumazim uan dag…®aba ko bizibar garava, a uab…® ua bagh bizitam givezan kogham.  
\v 12 Ingangarir gumaziba, me dagher av…®riba iti, o dagher muziariba iti, me d…®mangan derav…®ra dakuam. Ez…® dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazim, a zurara uan bizir av…®rir kabagh n…®ghn…®ghava, deraghav akuir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 13 K…® gara overiam…®n apengan itir arazibar garima, arazir bar kurar mam iti. Gumazir mam, g…®n izamin os…®mt…®zim…®n atiatigha pura tintinibar bizibagh ivezamin ifongiam d…®kab…®ragha, uan dag…®aba at…®gha deraghav…®ram dar gara iti.  
\v 14 Egha g…®n an dag…®ar ingangarim akuiaghir…®z…®, an dag…®aba bar g…®vaz…®ma, a uan borim dan…®ngamin biziba pu. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Jop 1:21; Onger Akaba 49:17; 1 Timoti 6:7\x*E fo, en amebam e batezir dughiam…®n, a bizitam saram e batezir puvat…®, e puram bibiabara iti. Kamagh…®ra, e ovengamin dughiam…®n, e pura bibiabara mangam. E guizbang…®ra bizir av…®riba iniasa ingangarir m…®t…®abagh ami, egh e aremeghamin dughiam…®n, e bizir katam sara Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n mangan kogham.  
\v 16 Ez…® kar uaghan bar os…®mt…®zir kurar mam, e pura dafarir k…®nibar nguazir kam…®n ize, ez…® kamagh…®ra, e dafarir k…®nibar uamategh mangam. Egha e nguazir kam…®n tir dughiam…®n, e pura ingangarir m…®t…®abagh ami, mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuav an suighan ibura.  
\v 17 Nguazir kam…®n tir dabirabim, a derazir pu, mati e zurara os…®mt…®zim ikia ovevem…®n m…®tarmem…®n aven apia dagheba api. E zurara navir kuram isava, atarava, ar…®mariaba isi.  
\v 18 Guizbang…®ra, k…® bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghua kamagh…®n fo, arazir mam bar deragha arazir kam gafira. Arazir kam, a kamak…®n, God e gan…®ngizir dughiar otevir overiam…®n apengan ikiamim…®n, e uan ingangarir e amizibar ivezim inigh daghebar am…® bar akuegh ikiam. Bar akongezir arazir kam, a ivezir God e bagha m…®sevezimra. 
\p  
\v 19 Eght…® God dag…®aba ko bizitaba gumazitam danight…®ma, a fogh suam, da ivezir God a bagha inabaziba. Egh an adar gan bar akuegh, egh uan ingangariba ko dabirabim…®n gan egh navir am…®rizim inigh ik…®t…®, kamagh…®n deragham. Bizir kaba, kar God an…®ngiz…® bizir aghuiba.  
\v 20 Egha God gumazir kam ataghiz…® a uan dabirabir aghuim…®n gara, bar akuegha mamagh…®ra ikia, kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir pu, k…® dughiar otevim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiam. 
\c 6  
\s1 Ik…®r…®m…®rir kam, os…®mt…®ziba an iti 
\p  
\v 1 K…® overiam…®n apengan ikia os…®mt…®zir kurar mam…®n garima, gumazamiziba aneterava ingangarir dafam gami.  
\v 2 God gumazir mam dag…®ar av…®riba ko, bizir av…®riba ko ziar ekiam, da a gan…®ngi, ez…® a ifongezir bizitam…®n otevezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazir kam, God a gan…®ngiz…® bizir aghuir kaba, an adar amu bar akuegh ikian f…®r…®n, God gumazir igharazim bizir kaba anetaghiz…® an ada inigha dagh amua bar akuegha iti. Arazir kam, a bar ikuvigha, an m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 3 Eght…® gumazitam borir 100pla ik…®va, nguazir kam…®n azenir av…®ribar ik…®, egh gumazir kam uan bizir aghuir kaba bagh bar akuegh ikian kogh, egh g…®n aremeght…®, me deragh a bagh mozim g…®kuigh anefaghan koght…®, arazir kam, a bar derazir puvat…®. K…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, borir amebam…®n navim…®n aven aremezim, a gumazir azenir av…®ribar nguazir kam…®n itim gafira.  
\v 4 Kamagh amir borim, mati pura bizim, a ziaba puvat…®z…®, me m…®tarmem…®n anefazir dughiam…®n, me a g…®namadagha g…®fa.  
\v 5 Egha borir kam, an aruer angazangarim…®n ganizir puvat…®gha, bizitam bar a g…®fozir puvat…®. Egha borir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n avughsazir aghuim gamua iti. Kamagh…®n, borir kam…®n dabirabim, gumazir bizir av…®riba itir kam…®n dabirabim gafira.  
\v 6 Gumazir kam uan bizir kabar gara, dagh agoir puvat…®. Gumazir kam 1,000…®n azeniba o 2,000…®n azenibar nguazir kam…®n ik…®t…®, an dabirabim, borir kam…®n dabirabim gafiraghan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, e bar mogh…®ram oveng nguibar vam…®ran mangam. 
\p  
\v 7 E dagheba iniasa, kamagh…®n, e zurara ingari. Ez…® dagher e isiba, da en ifongiam agevir puvat…®.  
\v 8 Manmagh…®n amiz…®, fofozir gumazim fofoziba puvat…®zir gumazim gafira? Bar puvat…®. Eght…® gumazir biziba puvat…®zim, arazir aghuim…®n gumazamizibar damazim…®n a damight…®, bizir kam manmagh…®n an akuraght…®, a ik…®v…®ra ikiamin ivezir aghuir manam iniam?  
\v 9 Gumazir maba ghaze, e bizir guar av…®riba inis…® n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Arazir kam uaghan an m…®ngariba aven mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si, mati gumazim am…®nim…®n suighasa ivegha ghuava an suighan ibura. Kamagh…®n dera, bizir tizir e inigha g…®vaziba, e dagh ifuegh dar suiragh ikiam. 
\p  
\v 10 Bizir otivir kaba, da puram otivir puvat…®. Bar fom…®ra God da otivasa m…®kemez…®, da dat…®r…®gh…®n otivaghiri. Egha God en arazibagh fogha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n e a ko uari batoghan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, an gavgavim en gavgavim gafira.  
\v 11 E fo, e m…®g…®r…®g…®ar adoghodozir av…®ribav k…®mt…®ma, da manmagh…®n en akurvagham? Bar puvat…®. Puv…®ra m…®geir arazim, a tong en akuraghan kogham, e pura m…®gei.  
\v 12 E dughiar bar otevim…®n nguazir kam…®n iti, ez…® en ik…®r…®m…®rim, a dagheba puvat…®gha uaghan an m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. En ik…®r…®m…®rim, mati ghuariam aruem apazaz…®ma, temer dughuazim zuam…®ram arav ghu. Ez…® tina kamagh…®n fo, e arazir aghuir manam…®n g…®nt…®gham? Ez…® tina kamagh…®n fo, e ovegh g…®vaght…®, bizir manaba overiam…®n apengan otivam? 
\c 7  
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir aghuir av…®riba 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 22:1\x*Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, n…® gumazir bar aghuim, n…®ghn…®zir kam a dera. Egha a borer aghuir ivezim bar p…®n itim gafira. Eght…® dughiar n…® ovengamim, a dughiar n…®n amebam n…® batezim gafiragham. 
\p  
\v 2 Gumazim aremeght…®, me a bagha azir d…®penir mam…®n ik…®t…®ma, n…® a bagh mang…®. Arazir kam, a me d…®penim ikia isar ekiabagh amir arazim gafira. Guizbang…®ra, e bar mogh…®ra ovengam. Kamagh…®n, e nguazir kam…®n ik…® bar derav…®ra ovevem…®n arazim g…®n…®ghn…®gham. 
\p  
\v 3 E bizitam bagh navim ikuvigh osemegh ik…®t…®, arazir kam akazir arazim gafira. Guizbang…®ra, navir os…®mt…®ziba, e gamima en guaba ikufi, arazir kam e gami e arazir aghuim g…®fofogha egha akonge. 
\p  
\v 4 Egha gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itim, an aremezir gumazim bagha azia itir darazi ko ikiam. Ez…® gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®ziba, me inivaf…®zir agoroger arazir av…®ribagh amir gumazamiziba ko ikiasa. 
\p  
\v 5 Gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, n…®n atar, n…® ak…®rm…®gham, n…® me baregh men g…®n mang…®t…® arazir kam a dera. Arazir kam, gumazir onganim ziar ekiam isa n…® gan…®dir arazim, gafiragham. 
\p  
\v 6 Egh gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®ziba ak…®t…®, men akazibar m…®ngariba puvat…®gham. Mati benir ataghatarim avim…®n ikia isia t…®ngazi, egha a m…®nem gamima a isir puvat…®. Arazir kam uaghan pura bizim, an m…®ngariba puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 7 Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ikiava gumazir igharazibar biziba ko dag…®aba, pura dagh ekua da isi, a mati gumazir onganim. Eght…® gumazim apezeperir dag…®aba init…®, an arazir kam…®n, a uab…® uan n…®ghn…®zir aghuim gas…®ghas…®si. 
\p  
\v 8 Eght…® gumazitam ingangarim foregh a damuasava ami, kar arazir aghuim. Egha an an ingarava aneg…®fa, arazir kam bar deragha arazir ingangarim damuasava amim, gafira. Ez…® gumazir navim am…®ragha uab…®n asugha n…®m…®ra itim, a dera. An arazim, gumazir uab…®ra uab…® fem…®n arazim, bar a gafira. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9 \xt Jems 1:19\x*N…® zuam…®ra gumazir munam…®n an…®ngagheghan mark…®. An…®ngagharim, a gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zim…®n arazim. 
\p  
\v 10 N…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®ma, dughiar fom…®ra ikezim, dat…®r…®gh…®n tir dughiam gafira?‚Äù Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim puvat…®zim, a kamagh…®n azangs…®gham. 
