\v 13 God amizir biziba, ia bar deraghv…®ra, dagh n…®ghn…®gh. Egh God bizitam damight…® a ik…®z…®r…®ght…®, tinara uam anem…®negham?  
\v 14 N…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n biziba bar derav…®ram otivt…®, n…® bar akuegh ik…®. Eght…® dughiar kuram n…® batoght…®, n…® kamagh…®n fogh suam, God dughiar aghuiba ko dughiar kuraba e bagha da amadi. Kamagh…®n, e fozir pu, bizir manam g…®n otivam. 
\p  
\v 15 K…® nguazir kam…®n ikia arazir av…®rav…®ribar gara ghaze, nan ik…®r…®m…®rim, an m…®ngariba mongez…® k…® dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. Egha k…® gumazir mabar garima, me arazir aghuibar g…®nt…®gha, egha ariaghire. Ez…® k…® gumazir mabar gari, me arazir kurabagh amua, egha dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n iti.  
\v 16 Kamagh…®n e uan damazim…®n uari f…®, arazir aghuim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim…®n g…®nt…®ghs…®, bar pamten ingaran kogham. E ti, uarira uarigh as…®ghasigham.  
\v 17 Egh e uaghan arazir kuraba ko arazir onganibar g…®nt…®ghs…® bar pamten ingaran kogham. E ti God ovengasa e bagha inabazir dughiam…®n av…®ragham.  
\v 18 N…® uab…® tuavir aghuim…®n g…®n mang…®, egh arazir aghuim…®n suiragh, egh arazir kuram…®n suighan mark…®. Gumazim God…®n atiatia an apengan iti, a bizir manam damut…®, a bar derav…®ram otogham. 
\p  
\v 19 Eght…® gumazir dapanir ekiar 10pla, nguibar ekiar mam…®n akuragh a damut…®, a tugh gavgavigham. Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim, a gumazitam…®n akuraght…®, a bar gavgavigh nguibar ekiar kam…®n gavgavim gafiragham. 
\p  
\v 20 God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumazitam, zurara arazir aghuitam gamir pu. A dughiar mabar uaghan arazir kurabagh ami. 
\p  
\v 21 N…® gumazamizibar akaba bar, da baraghan mark…®. Egh n…® kuarim at…®gh deragh me baraght…®, n…®n ingangarir gumazim ti akar kuram n…® dan…®ngam.  
\v 22 Guizbang…®ra, n…® kamagh…®n fogh, n…® uab…® dughiar av…®ribar akar kurabar gumazir igharazibav m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 23 K…® bar fofozir gumazim…®n otivasa, kamagh…®n k…® bizir kabar m…®ngariba bativasa bar derav…®ra da tuis…®gha dagh n…®ghn…®ki. Ez…® nan n…®ghn…®zim otefe.  
\v 24 Bizir otivir kabanang…®n m…®ngaribagh foghamin ingangarim, bar aven ko. Mati bizim bar saghon itima e a buri, o bar v…®n mar iti. Kamagh…®n, tinara bizir kabar m…®ngaribagh fogham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 25 K…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozir aghuibar m…®ngaribagh foghasa bar ingangarir dafam gami. Egha uaghan arazir kuraba ko arazir onganibar m…®ngaribagh foghasa ingangarir dafam gami. 
\p  
\v 26 K…® ingara ghua kamagh…®n fo, amizir maba os…®mt…®zir bar ekiaba e gan…®di, ez…® da ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim gafira. Amizir kabanang mati, gumaziba en suighamin iveba. Ez…® men dafariba mati sen e ik…®rarigham. God gumazitam gifueght…®, gumazir kam amizibar ivem gitagh ar…®mang…®gham. Eght…® ivem, arazir kurabagh amir gumazim…®n suiraght…®, an a gitaghan kogham. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 27 Ez…® fofozir gumazim kamagh…®n m…®gei, Bar guizbang…®ra, k…® bizir kabar m…®ngariba bativasa bar n…®m…®ra n…®m…®ra ingara ghua dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir mabar arazim g…®fo.  
\v 28 K…® ghua amiziba buriagha aruava amizir aghuitam bativasa ingara ghua tam batozir puvat…®. Ez…® tausen…®n gumazibar tong…®n, k…® gari, gumazir aghuir vabara iti. Egha k…® amizir aghuitam…®n garir puvat…®.  
\v 29 Egha k…® n…®ghn…®zir ekiar mam bato, a kamak…®n, God gumazamizibar ingarigha ghaze, me an damazim…®n dera. Ez…® me uari n…®ghn…®zir av…®riba ko tuavir guar av…®ribar g…®n zui. 
\c 8  
\p  
\v 1 Fofozir gumazamizibara bar bizibar m…®ngaribagh fos. Kamagh…®n tina men fofozim gafiragham? Guizbang…®ra, gumazim…®n navim ikuvight…® an guam m…®sigham, eght…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozir aghuim a damut…® an guam angazangarigh, bar akongegham. 
\s1 N…® atrivim…®n akam…®n g…®n mang…® 
\p  
\v 2 K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, n…® atrivim…®n akam…®n g…®n mang…®. N…® God ko d…®k…®r…®zir akam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh atrivim…®n akaba batoghan mark…®.  
\v 3 Egh n…® atrivim ko ik…® zuam…®ram anetagh…®raghan mark…®. Egh n…®n akaba ko atrivim…®n akaba uariv soght…®, n…® akaba gavgavan mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n fogh, atrivim n…® bareghan kogham, a uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mangam.  
\v 4 E bar fo, atrivim m…®k…®mt…®ma, gumazamiziba bar an akam…®n g…®n mang…®. Eght…® gumazitam kamagh…®n an azangs…®ghan kogham, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha kamagh…®n ami?‚Äù  
\v 5 Gumazir atrivim…®n akaba bar dar g…®nt…®zim, a derav…®ra ikiam. Eght…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itir gumazim, a bizibar amuamin tuavim ko dughiam g…®fogham.  
\v 6 E fo, e gumazamiziba en os…®mt…®ziba bar ekevez…® e da ateri. Ez…® da ak…®ramin tuavir aghuim ko da ak…®ramin dughiar aghuim iti.  
\v 7 E fozir pu, bizir manam g…®n otivam. Ez…® bizir kabar gun e m…®k…®mamin gumaziba puvat…®.  
\v 8 Gumazim ovengamin dughiam…®n, an duam an inivaf…®zim atagh…®ragham. Eght…® gumazitam an anogoreghan kogham, gavgavir kaba bar puvat…®. Gumazitam ovevem…®n dughiam gis…®vaghan kogham. E fo, m…®dorozim…®n dughiam…®n, m…®dorozir gumazir dapanir ekiaba, m…®dorozir gumaziba ateght…® me uamategh uan nguibabar mangan kogham. Egha gumazim arazir kuram…®n g…®nt…®si, an arazir kam bar an porogh, anetagh…®raghan iburagham. 
\s1 E bar akongezir arazim…®n g…®nt…®gham 
\p  
\v 9 K…® bizir kabar garava, gumazamizir overiam…®n apengan ikiava amir bizibagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. Egha dughiar kam…®n k…® garima, gumazir ekiar maba gumazamizir mabagh ativagha me d…®kab…®ra paza me gami.  
\v 10 Egha dughiar mabar k…® garima, gumazir kurar mam aremez…®, me mozim…®n anefa. Gumazamiziba anefagha uamategha gumazir kurar arazir kurabagh amim, aven itir nguibar ekiam…®n ghue. Egha me izir dughiar kam…®n, me gumazir kurar kam…®n ziam fe. Arazir kam uaghan, an m…®ngariba mongez…®, e dar gari puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si.\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Hibrun akam deragha ves 10…®n akabar m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 11 Dughiar mabar, gumazamiziba uan arazir kurabar ivezir kuram zuam…®ram a isir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n bizir kam gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®ziba fema, me arazir kurabar amuasa gavgavighav…®ra iti.  
\v 12 Dughiar mabar, gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, me arazir kurar av…®ribagh amuav…®ra iti, egha me dughiar bar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiava, me zuam…®ram oveir puvat…®. K…® fo, marazi kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazim God…®n atiatigh an apengan ik…®, derav…®ra ikiam.  
\v 13 Egh arazir kurabagh amir gumazim, a deragh ikian kogham. A God…®n atiatia an apengan itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n a bar dughiar otevim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 A guizbang…®ra, me onganigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ez…® k…® arazir mam…®n garima, a me m…®geir mogh…®n otozir puvat…®. Ez…® arazir kam, a bar onganigha bar ikufi. Dughiar mabar, gumazamizir God…®n damazim…®n deraziba, ivezir kurar gumazamizir kuraba iniamim isi. Ez…® gumazamizir kuraba, God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumazamizibar ivezim isi. Ez…® arazir kam, k…® ghaze, a uaghan an m…®ngarim modoz…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, e bar akueghamin arazim…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, a deragham. Ua tuavir aghuir e g…®nt…®ghamba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n e overiam…®n apengan ik…® dagheba ko d…®pabar am…®va bar akuegh ikiam. E fo, e ingangarir m…®t…®abagh ami, egh dughiar God e ataghiz…® e overiam…®n apengan itim…®n, e bar akongezir arazim damu ikiam. 
\p  
\v 16 K…® gumazamizibar ingangarir arazibar gara derav…®ra fofozim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim iniasa arueba ko d…®magaribar ingangarir bar dafam gamua akuir puvat…®.  
\v 17 Guizbang…®ra God biziba bar dar ingari, ez…® k…® dar ganigha fo, e nguazim…®n otivizir bizir kabar m…®ngariba buriva avegham. Egh e dagh foghs…®, ingar mang…® am…®ragham. Eght…® fofozir gumazamiziba suam, e dar m…®ngaribagh fogha g…®fa, me guizbang…®ra m…®geir puvat…®. Me dagh foghan kogham. 
\c 9  
\s1 Bizir kamra bar e bativam 
\p  
\v 1 K…® bizir kaba bagha derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha ghua kamagh…®n fos, God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumazamiziba ko, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba ko, me amir biziba, da bar God…®n agharim…®n iti. God uab…®, gumazamizibagh ifongezir arazim ko gumazamizibagh ifongezir puvat…®zir arazim gamiz…® da otifi. Guizbang…®ra, e gumazamiziba fozir pu, bizir tiziba g…®n otivam.  
\v 2 Ez…® bar e bativamin bizir mam iti, e gumazamizir God…®n damazim…®n deraziba, gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba, ko gumazir aghuiba, ko gumazir kuraba, God…®n damazim…®n zuezir darasi, ko God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir darasi, gumazir ofa gamiba, ko ofa gamir puvat…®ziba uaghara, bizir kamra bar me batogham. Bizir kamra, gumazir aghuiba ko gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba bativam. Bizir kamra, gumazir God ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiziba ko, gumazir God ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim damuasa atiatingiziba, a bar me batogham.  
\v 3 Egh e overiam…®n apengan itir gumazamiziba bar, bizir kurar kamra bar e batifi, a kamak…®n: ovevem. Gumazamiziba nguazim…®n itir dughiam…®n, me fo, me aremegham, egha dughiaba bar ovevem…®n arazim bagha n…®ghn…®gha navim osemegha bar onganigha a bagha m…®zuai. Egha g…®n me uaghan ariaghiri.  
\v 4-5 Afiar angam…®ra itim, laion…®n aremezim gafira. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, gumazamizir angam…®ra itiba, gumazamizir ariaghirezibagh afira. Me fo, bizitam me bativt…®, me ovengam. Ez…® gumazir ovengeziba, me bizitam g…®fozir puvat…®, egh me bizir aghuitam inian kogham. Ez…® gumaziba me g…®namadagha g…®fa.  
\v 6 Gumazamiziba ariaghirezir dughiam…®n, men ifongiam ko adariba ko gumazir igharazim…®n bizibagh ifongezir arazim, da bar g…®fa. Ez…® gumazamizir kaba, me ua overiam…®n apengan ik…® bizitam damuan kogham. 
\p  
\v 7 Aria, n…® mang…® dam…® bar akongegh. Egh n…® wain…®n d…®pam am…® navir am…®rizim inigh. God arazir kam…®n amamangat…®.  
\v 8 N…® zurara korotiar aghuibar aghu bar deragh kur…®k…® dapanar…®ziba batogh bar akuegh ik…®.  
\v 9 En ik…®r…®m…®rim mati pura bizim…®n m…®n itima an m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha bar okam n…®ghn…®si. Eght…®, God n…® gan…®ngizir ik…®r…®m…®rir kam, n…® overiam…®n apengan a m…®sevezir dughiabar, a ko bar akuegh ik…®. God a isa ivezir aghuim…®n m…®n n…® bagha anem…®sevegha n…® gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n n…® overiam…®n apengan ik…®, uan ingangaribar amuva, God n…® gan…®ngizir ik…®r…®m…®rim amuir aghuim…®n m…®n a ko ik…® bar akongegham.  
\v 10 Egh n…® ingangaritam damus…®, bar uan gavgavim sara a damu. N…® fo, Oveaghuezibar Nguibar n…® mangamim, n…® ingangarir tam ko n…®ghn…®zitam damuan kogham. Danganir kam…®n, n…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuitam ko fofozir aghuitam inian kogham. 
\p  
\v 11 K…® uamategha overiam…®n apengan bizir mam…®n gari. Gumazir bar puv…®ra atamra ivemariba, me dughiar mabar gumazir igharazibagh afirazir pu. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, dughiar mabar uan apanibagh afirazir puvat…®. Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, ko fofozir ekiaba itiba, me dughiar mabar dag…®aba ko bizir av…®riba isir puvat…®. Ez…® ingangarir guar av…®ribagh amir fozir gumaziba, me dughiar mabar ingangarir ekiaba isir puvat…®. E fo, dughiar kuram dughiatabar bar e bativam.  
\v 12 E fozir pu, e dughiar manam os…®mt…®zim e bativam. Ez…® dughiar kuram zuam…®ram e batifi, mati kuarazim o osirim ivem…®n aven ghuz…® an an suiragha iti. 
\s1 Gumazamizibar arazir aghuim ko arazir kuram 
\p  
\v 13 K…® overiam…®n apengan ikia ua bizir mam…®n garima an oto. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, kar ti, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itim…®n nedazir bar aghuim. Bizir k…® garim kamak…®n.  
\v 14 Dughiar mam nguibar muziarir mam iti, ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba an itir puvat…®. Ez…® atrivir bar gavgavir mam uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha a ko m…®sogh a d…®kab…®nasa ize. Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba nguibar kam bar anek…®arugha, an d…®vazir gavgavim akarasa bizibar ak…®ri.  
\v 15 Ez…® nguibar kam…®n, biziba puvat…®zir gumazir mam iti. Gumazir kam, n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozim iti. Egha an n…®ghn…®zir aghuim…®n, a nguibar kam uan apaniba dam a iniasa tuaviba buriz…®, me derav…®ram oto. Egha g…®n gumaziba ua biziba puvat…®zir gumazir kam, me a g…®namada.  
\v 16 Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®masa, n…®ghn…®zir aghuim, gavgavir ekiam gafira. Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir biziba puvat…®zim, an n…®ghn…®zir aghuim pura bizir k…®nim…®n m…®n iti. Kamagh…®n me an akaba barazir puvat…®. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 17 Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itim uan akabar asughasugh n…®m…®ra m…®k…®mt…®, e da baraght…®, deragham. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amir gumazim…®n akaba, da n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zir gumazibar atrivim, 
\q3 an tiarir arozim gafira. 
\q1  
\v 18 N…®ghn…®zir aghuim, a m…®dorozim…®n bizibagh afira. 
\q2 Eght…® gumazitam arazir kurar tam damight…®, 
\q3 an arazir aghuir av…®rim gas…®ghasigham. 
\b  
\c 10  
\p  
\v 1 E fo, bereziba mughuriar aghuim zuir borem…®n s…®vafarim…®n aven mag…®r…® ar…®ghireght…®, borer kam bar puv…®ra mughagham. Kamagh…®ra arazir onganir muziarim, gumazim…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko ziar ekiam d…®kab…®ragham. 
\p  
\v 2 Gumazir uan navim…®n aven n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itim, an arazir aghuibagh ami. Ez…® gumazir uan navim…®n aven n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itir puvat…®zim, an onganigha arazir kurabagh ami.  
\v 3 Egh gumazir kam pura tuavim…®n darut…®, an arazibara gumazir mabar akakagh suam, a n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 4 Eght…® n…®n gumazir dapanim n…®n atart…®, n…® uan ingangarim atagh…®raghan mark…®. A fogh suam, n…® os…®mt…®zim iti. Egh n…® n…®m…®ra ik…®t…®, a n…®n arazir kuram g…®namadagham. 
\p  
\v 5 K…® overiam…®n apengan ikia ua garima, gumazir maba os…®mt…®zir bar dafar mam gami. Ez…® os…®mt…®zir kurar kam, a gumazir dapanibar os…®mt…®zimra.  
\v 6 Gumazir dapaniba, dughiar mabar ingangarir ekiaba isa gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zibagh an…®di. Egha dughiar mabar ingangarir mong derazir puvat…®ziba isa dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazamizibagh an…®di.  
\v 7 Ez…® k…® garima, ingangarir gumazir k…®niba, hoziabagh is…®n apiagha zuima, gumazir ekiaba mati ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n suebar zui. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 10:8 \xt Onger Akaba 7:15; Aghuzir Akaba 26:27\x*Gumazir tam mozir ekiam g…®kuigh a ti uab…® an mag…®r…®gham. Eght…® gumazitam me dag…®abar ingarizir d…®vazir gavgavim abight…®, kuruzim ti a givigham.  
