\v 10 Eght…® gumazim…®n sobiam ghumighan koght…®, an anem…®neghan kogh, a temem ok…®s…® ingangarir dafam damigham. Eght…® gumazim n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ik…®va, a ingangarir aghuim damut…®, an ingangarim…®n dagher aghuim otogham.  
\v 11 Eght…® gumazim kuruzim damight…® a n…®m…®ra ikiamin arazim g…®fogh, a deragham. Egh a kuruzim ateght…®, an a givight…®, an fofozim manmagh…®n an akuragham? Bar puvat…®.  
