\v 13 Egh gumazir kam d…®kavigh m…®k…®m…®va, a paz…® bizir onganibav m…®k…®mam. Eght…® an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba g…®vamin dughiam…®n, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar ikuvigham, mati gumazir bar onganim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba.  
\v 14 Ez…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®ziba, me m…®g…®a mamagh…®ra iti. E fozir puvat…®, bizir manam g…®n otivam. Egha e fozir puvat…®, bizir manam e aremegh g…®vaght…®, a g…®n nguazim…®n otivam. 
\p  
\v 15 Gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba bar puvat…®zim uan d…®penim…®n mangasa tuaviba buriava avenge. Kamagh…®n amir gumazim, a pura ingangarir m…®t…®abagh amua, an gavgavim pura gefi. 
