\v 16 O gumazamizir ian kantrin atrivim agh…®rimra itim, Iavzika! Ian gumazir faragha zuiba ti m…®zarazibara d…®kava pura isabara amuv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® os…®mt…®zir ekiabara ian kantrin kam bativam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 31:4\x*Eght…® ian kantrin atrivim, a gumazir ziam itir tam…®n borim, eght…® ian gumazir faragha zuiba, me dagheba ko wain…®n d…®paba apir dughiam…®n da am…® gavgavim uari dan…®ngam, egh d…®par onganir av…®riba apir arazibar amuan kogham, eght…® kantrin kam, a bar derav…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 18 Eght…® gumazim am…®ragh uan d…®penir inogorim ak…®ran aghuaght…®, d…®penir inogorim angarigh…®reght…®, amozim aven ir…® d…®penim gas…®ghasigham. 
\p  
\v 19 Daghem a gumazim gamima, a bar akonge, ez…® wain…®n d…®pam gumazim gamima, an navim bar nuira. Ez…® dag…®aba da ingangarir guar av…®rim damuamin bizir aghuim. 
\p  
\v 20 N…® uan akuir danganim…®n aven modogh…®v ik…®, adarir kurabar atrivim ko dag…®aba itir gumazim, aning damuan mark…®. Egh n…® uaghan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurabar me damuan mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n damut…®, kuarazitam ti n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba inigh mang…® me danigham. 
\c 11  
\s1 N…® deragh n…®ghnigh…®va ingangarim damu 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 11:1 \xt Aisaia 32:20; Matyu 10:42; Galesia 6:9-10; Hibru 6:10\x*N…® danganir av…®ribar ingangaribar amu, egh n…® g…®n ivezir aghuim iniam.  
\v 2 N…® fozir pu, dughiar kurar manam nguazir kam…®n otivam. Kamagh…®n, n…® uan dag…®aba is…® 7pla o 8plan dag…®ar ingangaribar ar…®kigh. 
\p  
\v 3 E fo, d…®pam overiam…®n p…®n itir ghuariabagh iz…®vaz…®ma, amozim nguazim giri. Temem ira saut…®n amadaghan ir…®ghav iti, o not…®n amadaghan ir…®ghav iti, a danganir ir…®zim…®n, a ir…®gh…®v ikiam.  
\v 4 Eght…® n…® am…®nim ko amozim…®n dughiam bagh aning m…®zuam mang…® azenitam…®n ingarigh an oparighan kogh, n…® daghetam inian kogham.  
\v 5 God biziba bar dar ingari, ez…® e kamagh…®n fozir pu, manmagh amiz…®, borir igiam, amebam…®n navim…®n aven iti, ez…® an duam iza an aven ghuz…®ma an angam…®ra iti. Kamagh…®ra God amir biziba, e dagh foghan kogham.  
\v 6 N…® daghetaba m…®zarazim…®n da opar…®va, taba guarat…®zim…®n da opar, n…® kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, dagher n…® m…®zarazim…®n opariziba o n…® guarat…®zim…®n opariziba derav…®ram otivigham, o da uaghara derav…®ram otivam. 
\p  
\v 7 Angazangarim a bizir aghuim, ez…® e aruem…®n angazangarim…®n gara, bar akonge.  
\v 8 N…® nguazir kam…®n itir azenibar, n…® bar akuegh ik…®. Egh e azenir av…®ribar ik…®, bizir kaba bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, e bar azenir av…®ribar, m…®tarmem…®n ik…® Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n ikiam. Ez…® bizir g…®n otivamiba, dar m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\s1 Gumazamizir igiabar sure damuamin akaba 
\p  
\v 9 Ia gumazamizir igiaba, ia igiamra itir dughiam…®n, ia bar akongegh ik…®. Ia uan n…®ghn…®ziba ko ifongiam…®n g…®nt…®gh. Kamagh…®n ia uari bagh gan, God uan kotiam…®n dughiam, a ian araziba tuis…®gham. 
\p  
\v 10 Ia igiamra itir dughiam, a ruarazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, bizir os…®mt…®ziba ia gan…®diba, ia puv dagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Egh ia, bizir m…®zazir ian m…®karzibagh an…®dibar g…®nt…®ghan mark…®. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, ia igiam…®n itir ik…®r…®m…®rim uaghan, mati an m…®ngariba mongez…® e dagh fozir puvat…®gha okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\c 12  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1 \xt 2 Samuel 19:35; Aghuzir Akaba 22:6; Azir Akam 3:27\x*God bar en ingari, kamagh…®n, ia igiamra itir dughiam…®n, ia a g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Ia kamagh…®n a g…®n amadagh g…®n ghuright…®, dughiar kuram ia batoght…®, ia vaghvagh kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúK…® uan ik…®r…®m…®rim gakongezir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 2 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n ian damaziba ikuvight…®ma, ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, aruem ko iak…®nim ko m…®koveziba deragha isir puvat…®. Ez…® amozir ghuariam ua iza danganir vam…®ran iti.  
\v 3 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, ian dafariba gavgaviba puvat…®gh in…®gham. Eght…® ian sueba gavgaviba puvat…®gh ik…®z…®righam. Eght…® ian atariba bar asighiregh vaghvaziba ik…®t…®, ia dagher gavgavibar aman kogham. Egh ian damaziba ikuvight…®, ia derav…®ra bizibar ganan kogham.  
\v 4 Egh ian kuarir toribar bar p…®right…®, ia d…®penim…®n azenan otivir n…®g…®niba baraghan kogham, mati me wit m…®rm…®rir dag…®am…®n t…®ngagharim, ko marvir ararer av…®riba. Eght…® ia dakuamin dughiam…®n, kuarazibar ararem…®ra ia gaghunam.  
\v 5 Eght…® ia danganir p…®n itibar atiating…®va, tuavibar aruan buraghburegham. Ian dapanar…®ziba ghurghuright…®, ia daruan asaghasegham. Eght…® biziba ia damut…®, ian naviba da bagh d…®kavan kogham. Eght…® ia aremegh mang…® nguibar ia zurara ikiamim…®n ikiam. Eght…® ian nguibam…®n iti darasi, me arang azir akabar amu ikiam. 
\p  
\v 6 Ia t…®ghar aremeghamin dughiam…®n, ia God g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Guizbang…®ra, ia kamagh…®n ovengam, mati lam…®n silvan sen dutuaghir…®z…®, an gol…®n itarim ir…®gha ikuviz…®, an avir angazangarim munge. Egha mati, me mozir d…®pam…®n m…®nem dafagha d…®pam tua a gekuava anadir benim dutuaghir…®z…®, nguazir m…®ner d…®pam tuim, ir…®gha bar m…®saraghire.\f + \fr 12:6 \ft Hibrun akam…®n ves 2-6 da akar is…®n zuibara m…®gei, ez…® akar kabar m…®ngariba da deragha otozir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 7 E fo, God fom…®ra nguazir m…®nemeniam isa gumazim…®n ingari. Eght…® g…®n ia aremeght…® ian m…®karziba ua nguazir m…®nemeniam gavagham. Eght…® ian duar God ia gan…®ngiziba, uamategh God bagh mangam. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 8 Fofozir gumazim kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\q2 Biziba bar, dar m…®ngariba bar mongez…® 
\q2 e dagh fozir puvat…®gha bar okam n…®ghn…®si. 
\s1 Ak…®nafarim…®n akar abuananam 
\p  
\v 9 Fofozir gumazir kam bar n…®ghn…®zir aghuim iti, kamagh…®n a gumazamizibar sure gami. An akar aghuiba ko aghuzir akar av…®riba bar derav…®ra dagh n…®ghn…®gha da tuis…®si. Egh an akar manam gin…®ghn…®ght…®, a guizbang…®ra m…®k…®mt…®, an ak…®nafarim…®n an osiram.  
\v 10 Egha an akar aghuiba buria akar gumazamizibar kuaribar is…®ngiziba bagha ingangarir dafam gami. Egha bar derav…®ra guiz…®n akar kaba osiri. 
\p  
\v 11 Fofozir gumazim…®n akaba mati aghorim, me anem…®nez…® a ghumi. Aghorir kam, mati sipsipbar garir gumazim an suiragha sipsipbagh eghuva tuavim dar akakasi. Egha fofozir gumazim akar aghuiba akumakua ak…®nafarim…®n aven da osiri, eght…® akar kaba bar dughiar ruarim…®n ikiam, mati d…®koniba me palang gafuz…® da gavgafi. God bar en garir gumazim, egha akar kaba e gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 12 Nan borim, k…® akar abuananam ua n…® m…®k…®masa. N…® nan akam baragh. Gumazamiziba ak…®nafarir av…®riba osiri, ez…® ingangarir kamagh…®n amim a gevir puvat…®. N…® zurara ak…®nafaribar gant…®, n…®n m…®karzim bar am…®ragham. Kamagh…®n n…® bizir kam bagh derav…®ra gan. 
