\v 13 K…®, n…®ghn…®zir kaba bar dar gun n…® m…®kemegha g…®vagha, egha n…®ghn…®zir abuananam n…® m…®k…®masa. Egh akar kaba bar ada g…®vasa, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, e gumazamiziba en ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n faragha zuir bizim, a kamak…®n. E God…®n atiating an apengan ik…®, an akabar g…®nt…®gham.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 12:14 \xt Fofozir Gumazim 11:9; Aposel 17:30-31; Rom 2:16; 2 Korin 5:10\x*Guizbang…®ra, God e amizir araziba bagh uan kot…®n aven e tuis…®gham. Arazir aghuiba, ko arazir kuraba, ko mogava amir araziba sara da bagh e tuis…®gham.